               (list @tt{proc (f) zero?((f f))}   @${t_0 = t_f \to t_1})
               (list @tt{zero?((f f))}            @${t_1 = @tt{bool}})
               (list ""                           @${t_2 = @tt{int}})
               (list @tt{(f f)}                   @${t_f = t_f \to t_2}))]

然后，我们仍像之前那样求解：

